mul_right_bijective₀:
theorem _root_.mul_right_bijective₀ (a : G) (ha : a ≠ 0) : function.bijective ((· * a) : G → G) :=
  (Equiv.mulRight₀ a ha).bijective
#align mul_right_bijective₀ mul_right_bijective₀
